maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Joy
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Joy

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Did you notice that strange device next to the Inn-Keeper?
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Ты заметила странное устройство рядом с хозяйкой гостиницы?

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Always wondered what that is.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Всегда было интересно, что это такое.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Oh, that's a Ball-Recharger!
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Ах, это Шаро-зарядка.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Come again?
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Что-что?

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Yeah, I forgot you joined CrossWorlds a bit later.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Ой, я и забыла, что ты присоединилась к игре чуть позже.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: In the first release, you had to recharge your balls once you ran out of stamina.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: В первой версии приходилось перезаряжать свои шары, как только у тебя кончалась выносливость.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: There was even an extra gauge for that in the HUD.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: В интерфейсе даже была дополнительная шкала.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Really? Wow, I can't imagine having fun doing that.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: В самом деле? Вау, представляю, как "весело" это было.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: That's why they removed it, I guess. No one was happy.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Вот потому-то они её и убрали, я полагаю. Никому она не нравилась.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: But they keep this asset in as a reminder of the old times.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Но они оставили этот аппарат в качестве напоминания о былых временах.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Jock
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Джок

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Guid day, Lea!
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Приветштвую, Лея!
...Привет?!

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Kehahaha. Dornt fash yerse quine. Jean tauld me aw abit ye!
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Кехахаха. Не штоит бешпокоитша. Джина рашкасала мне вшё о тебе!

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Jock
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Джок

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Aam \c[3]Jock\c[0]!
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Йа \c[3]Джок\c[0]!

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Shocker fur ye, huh? Heard yer speech module is broken.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Ты потряшена, не так ли? Шлышал, твой рещевой модуль шломан.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Ye swatch loch th' cheerful lassie nonetheless.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: И тем не менее, ты оштаёшша такхой вешёлой девщонкой!

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Keha, sae ye want tae ken somethin' abit th' \c[3]legendary bunny\c[0], aye?
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Кеха, шож, ти хощиш уснать щото о \c[3]легендарном кролике\c[0], дак?

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: [nods]
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: [кивает]

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Alrecht, haur is whit Ah ken!
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Отлищно, вот ш этъим я могху помощь!

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Ah heard, ye need tae fin' some sort ay roon capture device.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Я шлышал, вам нушно щто-тъо вроте ущтройштфа длья захфатъа.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Ye can teel Jean Ah micht hae foond thes device, but she still needs somethin' else.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Ты мошешь шкасать Джине, што я, кхашется, нашёл этъо уштройштфо, но ей вшё нушно што-тъо ещё.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: But ah dunnae ken whit 'at is, kehahaha.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Но я не снаю, щто этъо именно, кехахаха.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Ah will send Jean aw th' details.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Я пошлю Джине вше потробноштъи.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Ye micht foond it mair when ye gab tae uir triblader mukker.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Вы мошете нахйтъи ефо, ешли погхофоритъе ш тругхом триблейдером.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: [nods]
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: [кивает]

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Jock
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Джок

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Awrite Lea, Ah send everythin' tae Jean.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Вшё ф порядкхе, Леа, я отправлю вшё Джине.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: [nods]
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: [кивает]

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Joe the Younger
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Джо младший

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Joe the Younger
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Джо младший

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Hi.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Привет.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Oh boy, a \v[lore.title.seeker]!\. So cool to finally meet one!
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Ничего себе, \v[lore.title.seeker]!\. Так круто встретить одного из вас!

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Hi?!
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Привет?!

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: I asked for help with a really awesome investigation but you're the first to volunteer!
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Я попросил помощи в потрясающем расследовании, но ты первая, кто вызвалась помочь!

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Well... you are, right?\. It's about some new species of \v[combat.name.hedgehog], how cool is that? Come on!
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Ну... ты ведь поэтому пришла, да?\. Это насчёт какого-то нового вида Дикоборзов, разве не круто? Давай!

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: [nods]
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: [кивает]

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Amazing, I see that you're with me on this!\. A true explorer!
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Потрясно, ты поможешь мне с этим!\. Истинный исследователь!

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Now, listen.\. We gotta go after this tribe of \v[combat.name.hedgehog]s I saw on an expedition recently.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Теперь, слушай.\. Мы должны проследовать за этим племенем Дикоборзов, которое я видел в экспедиции недавно.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Hey, wait!\. It's not just your normal-type \v[combat.name.hedgehog]s, oh no!
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Эй, погоди!\. Это не обычные Дикоборзы, нет!

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: The ones I saw must have evolved into a previously unseen \c[3]Flying-type\c[0]!
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Эти, которых я видел, должно быть, эволюционировали в ранее невиданный \c[3]летающий вид\c[0]!

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: I know, right?!\. No one believed me without proof and it wasn't like I could follow their footprints!
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Да, представляешь?!\. Никто не поверил мне без доказательств, а я же не мог пойти по их следам!

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Now this is where you come in!\. You will need to check out \c[3]Off Road 2\c[0] in \c[3]\v[area.autumn-area.name]\c[0].
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Вот тут ты и вступаешь!\. Тебе нужно проверить \c[3]Бездорожье 2\c[0] в \c[3]Расцвете Осени\c[0].

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: I saw them grazing there before they flew away, so I'm sure that they'll return!\. Please go there quickly.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Я видел, как они паслись там перед тем, как улететь, так что я уверен, что они вернутся!\. Пожалуйста, поторопись туда.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Great!\. I will do some more searching on my own.\. We'll stay in touch over \c[3]\v[lore.title.direct-link]\c[0]!
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Замечательно!\. Я тут сам ещё немного поищу.\. Оставайся на \c[3]Прямой связи\c[0]!

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Bye.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Пока.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: [shakes head]
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: [мотает головой]

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Whaaat?\. But you got me all excited and everything.\. Let's at least exchange numbers to stay in touch!
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Чтооо?\. Но ты меня так обрадовала и всё такое.\. Давай хотя бы обменяемся данными, чтобы оставаться на связи!

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: ...bye.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: ...пока.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Joe the Younger
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Джо младший

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Hi.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Привет.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Hey \v[lore.title.seeker].\. Please hurry and check out \c[3]Off Road 2\c[0] in \c[3]\v[area.autumn-area.name]\c[0].
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Привет, Искатель.\. Пожалуйста, поторопись и проверь \c[3]Бездорожье 2\c[0] в \c[3]Расцвете Осени\c[0].

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: I will continue my searching on my own.\. We will stay in touch over \c[3]\v[lore.title.direct-link]\c[0]!
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Я продолжу свои поиски самостоятельно.\. Держи контакт через \c[3]Прямую связь\c[0]!

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Joe the Younger
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Джо младший

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Hi.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Привет.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: \v[lore.title.seeker]!\. There you are again!
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Искатель!\. Ты снова здесь!

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: [nods]
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: [кивает]

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: I have already written a report based on your adventure with the \c[3]Flying-types and their king.\. \c[0]
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Я уже написал отчёт, основанный на твоих приключениях с \c[3]летающим видом и их королём\c[0].

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: All those people who didn't believe me will be in for a surprise, I tell ya!\. It will rock their shorts off!
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Всех тех людей, которые мне не верили, ждёт сюрприз, я тебе говорю!\. Это перевернёт их представление!

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: That crown will be a nice trophy as well.\. Always helps to have something shiny to show.
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Эта корона тоже будет хорошим трофеем.\. Всегда полезно иметь что-то блестящее напоказ.

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Thank you so much for your help, \v[lore.title.seeker]. I can't give you a badge but I hope this will do for a reward!
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Большое спасибо за твою помощь, Искатель. Я не могу дать тебе значок, но надеюсь, что и это сойдёт за награду!

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: [nods]
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: [кивает]

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Bye!
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Пока!

maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.orig: Yep, yep, see you around!
maps/rookie-harbor/inner-inn.json/entiti.text: Да, да, увидимся!
